doctype html
html
  head
    title Garage-PI
  body
    h1 Garage-PI

    form(action="/install/seed", method="POST")
      input(type="submit", value="1. Populate test data")
      
    p 2. When the DB data has been populated, you will se a QRCode here.

    if user
      p
        div Username: #{user.name}
        img(src=imgdata)
      form(action="/api/auth", method="POST")
        input(type="hidden", name="username", value="Test")
        input(type="input", placeholder="Insert QRCode string here", name="password")
        input(type="submit", value="2. Authenticate (get token)")
      
      form(action="/api/door/1/toggle", method="POST")
        input(type="input", placeholder="Insert token here", name="token")
        input(type="submit", value="3. Toggle door authenticated API call")